 up to 10% with less than 20% increase in vehicle mileage. Our findings\noutline that the value of redistribution is contingent on localised market\nstructure and customer behaviour.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 Jun 2020 14:52:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Dec 2020 18:20:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-29"}
