ations. The inhibition rates range from 75.56% to 91.11% for\nT. durum wheat irrigate at 80% to 100%, but are only 55.56% to 77.78% for\nbarley seeds treated with the same concentrations (80% to 100%).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 Jun 2020 15:41:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-16"}
